==Finnish==

====Etymology====
From the same Uralic root ''*ku'' as Hungarian [[hogy]]

===Conjunction===
'''kuin'''

#[[than]]
#:''Kissa on suurempi '''kuin''' hiiri.'' (Cat is larger than mouse.)
#[[as]], [[like]]
#:''Se kävelee '''kuin''' ankka.'' (It walks like a duck.)

